data.name: textBox4.Text
data.value: How to Use: 1) Enter email and password, and username to snipe. a) If blocking onto a non-premium, check the "Block" checkbox. b) If you don't know what name to snipe, check out the "Browse Names" button. 2) Set number of attempts. If you don't know what it should be, leave it alone. 3) Log in to the web browser on the right. Use the same account on the left. 4) Press "Start", and wait to see!
